name: The Hall Furniture Series : Complete Collection
description: The Hall Furniture Series : A complete collection of sofa, armchair, and coffee table for your metaverse home brought to you by Santuari Studio. Bringing new organic and synthetic life to your metaverse home studio. We first introduced this selection in the 3020’s. With the latest quantum technologies ahead of its time, this is the best way to experiencing life in post-human environments. With the auto-adjust feature, you can find your perfect definition of comfort within the fine Santuarian Silk main material.
